dfischer.utils

Class ParseUrlCgi

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.ParseUrl
      • dfischer.utils.ParseUrlCgi

  • public class ParseUrlCgi
extends ParseUrl
    Parses an URL and extracts the protocol, the host, the port, the file and all CGI parameter. Removes also an (optional) URL rewrite parameter/value from the file name.

      • getFileAndParameterNameKey

        public java.lang.String getFileAndParameterNameKey()

        Example:
        The url "https://www.zzz.dom/myFile?asdas=44&x=2&city=bern&country=ch"
        returns the key-value "myFile?asdas&x&city&country"
        Returns:
